==Format==
* '''Group Stage'''
** Four groups of three teams each
** Single round-robin, all matches are {{abbr/Bo1}}
** <span class="bg-up">Top two teams</span> from each group advance to the playoffs
** <span class="bg-down">Bottom team</span> is eliminated
* '''Playoffs'''
** Single-elimination bracket
** All matches are {{abbr/Bo1}}

